growth_dt <- fread("~/s3-roybal-tcsl/lenti_screen_compiled_data/data/invivo/tcsl155_growth.csv")

growth_dt <- rbind(
    unique(growth_dt[, list(
        day=0, cage, mouse, car, 
        length=0, width=0, height=0, 
        notes='', Area=0, Area2=0)]),
    growth_dt)

growth_summ_dt <- data.table(growth_dt)[, {
    bps= boxplot.stats(log(Area))$stats
    list(lo=bps[1],lhinge=bps[2],uhinge=bps[3],hi=bps[4])
    },
    by=.(car, day)]

ggplot(growth_dt, aes(x=car, y=Area2, color=day)) + geom_boxplot() + geom_jitter() + facet_grid(day~.)

ggplot(growth_dt) + geom_line(aes(y=log(Area2), x=day, color=car, group=interaction(mouse, cage))) + facet_wrap(.~car) + geom_ribbon(data=growth_summ_dt, aes(x=day, ymin=lo, ymax=hi, color=car, fill=car), alpha=0.2)
